            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01843.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <address><addrLine>Meltonsville, Alabama</addrLine></address>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1875-04-26">April 26 1875</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute><unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">Walt Whitman</unclear></salute>
            </opener>

            <p>It is sometimes very hard to <unclear  resp="#nnk" reason="illegible" cert="low">determine</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">who</unclear> ought or ought not to do or say or <gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="high" resp="#nnk">I</unclear> feel it rather proper or necessary for me to <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">write</unclear> you a letter now and do the best I can. <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">Along</unclear> with the parcel of papers which you sent me after getting my <hi rend="underline"><unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">baby's</unclear> letter</hi> I got the picture and the double column bill previously sent me in the New Republic's regular issue (that is the matter of it) about Foreign <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">lectures</unclear> on an American Poet. The last paragraph speaks of <hi rend="underline">"indigence"</hi> and I now write because of that. Let me guess why you <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">gave</unclear> <hi rend="underline">authority to that statement</hi>&#8212;I think it <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">rather</unclear> probable that you did so as a sort of <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">explanation</unclear> of the reason or a hint of the fact that <gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> not able to offer the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#js">bill.</unclear> <hi rend="underline">Walt</hi> <gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> <hi rend="underline">present or keepsake</hi> as would be <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">suited</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> <hi rend="underline">dignity</hi> or <hi rend="underline">exalted <unclear resp="#nnk" reason="illegible" cert="low">world</unclear></hi> the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">past</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> that light I could be<gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> of your <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> wish you were too poor to <hi rend="underline">raise</hi> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> pay postage even on your <gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> If <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">you</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="one worda"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">know</unclear> me well, one of the <gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> 
           
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01843.002.jpg" type="verso"/>
                <note type="authorial" place="bottom" anchored="true"><gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/><unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">for</unclear> the past, a rude but strong expression <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> your work <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> that <hi rend="underline">you heard me</hi>!! I think <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> myself <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">best</unclear> </note>
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> would be a remarkable <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/>, or <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> <hi rend="underline"> of riches</hi>, show, dress, <gap reason="illegible" extent="three or four words"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">described</unclear> absolutely by good <unclear resp="#nnk" reason="illegible" cert="low">sense</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="three or four words"/></p>
                    
                    
            <p>Leaving off that supposition, <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">, it</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> taken <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> you wanted me to post the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">bill as a sort</unclear> of advertisement of your books. (When I <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">was at</unclear> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">"town</unclear>" (<gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/>) two weeks ago, I sent money to <hi rend="underline"><unclear reason="illegible" cert="high" resp="#nnk">Butts &amp; Co.</unclear></hi> for a copy of Leaves of Grass to pass around among the folks there as a specimen&#8212;hoping, yet scarcely expecting to do much in behalf of increased sales of the same&#8212;</p>
            
            <p>The third supposition must naturally be that my <hi rend="underline">real good-will</hi> is now tested. I send a bill of money which is yours and you shall have a good deal more if you positively need it. I have <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">yet</unclear> on hand <hi rend="underline">two big bales of my cotton crop</hi> intended for spending money for the <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/>&#8212;sold <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">the other</unclear> of my crop (three more <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">big</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> one <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> to get interest. Friend! <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> neither <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> nor "dog poor"&#8212;<unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#js">I am a</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/>&#8212;<gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/>a good farm, and <hi rend="underline">some<gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/></hi> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">dollars</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">hands</unclear> of relatives and friends <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> <hi rend="underline">will</hi> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> I ever get to producing <gap reason="illegible" extent=" three or four words"/> wife, and little ones <gap reason="illegible" extent="three or four words"/> horse<!-- or "home?" -JS -->"
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.01843.003.jpg" type="recto"/>
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="three or four words"/> money to pay taxes and <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> our <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> our tenants make for us <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">all</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> grain <gap reason="illegible" extent="three or four words"/> lack only a little of <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> self&#8212;supp<gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> and need draw but lightly <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> our <hi rend="underline"><gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> fund</hi>, and when the crowd of <hi rend="underline">athletic</hi> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> boys shall grow a littler larger. I hope to <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">of</unclear> more land and "make things happen"&#8212;Now, I can see clearly (as I think) that <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">friendship</unclear> with or assistance to Walt Whitman, if he needs, is about the <hi rend="underline">best bid</hi> that any common man can make for immortality for himself and pleasure to his posterity&#8212;if intellectual retrogression of mankind is ahead of us it will not be.</p>
            <p>If the first supposition is correct, or the bill was <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">only</unclear> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#js">accidentally</unclear> put in the package of papers &amp; <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> do this way&#8212;<unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">clearly</unclear>you are not <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">rich</unclear> <!-- the only reason I see "rich" is that I believe the word I make out ends with an "h" and appears to begin with an "r" -NNK --> and I am not poor to hurt&#8212;you <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">have</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#js">sending</unclear> me papers &amp;c <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">requesting</unclear> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">an</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="three or four words"/>&#8212;if you have <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#js">reason enough</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> or through kindness of immensely <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> or relatives) to <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">live</unclear> as <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">will do</unclear> you <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> if you are content to <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/>
           
            <note type="authorial" place="bottom" anchored="true"><gap reason="illegible" extent="four or five words"/> desire to say "bully boy" <gap reason="illegible" extent="seven or eight words"/> Book always away from <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/></note>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.01843.004.jpg" type="verso"/>
            
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> by a continuance of past <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> would <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> to have you use the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#js">money</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> books, <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">magazines</unclear> or papers such as <hi rend="underline">you <gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> like to read <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">most</unclear></hi> and afterwards send to <gap reason="illegible" extent="1 word"/>. <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">I don't</unclear> care for scientific works (<hi rend="underline">except new works about mental or moral Philosophy</hi>)&#8212;I don't want political works, nor books of Poetry&#8212;I have not been such an enthusiast about Poetry as you might think, except that I have been <hi rend="underline">almost insane</hi> about <hi rend="underline">yours</hi> because you have so well expressed "<hi rend="underline">my sentiments exactly</hi>" (However, you don't convert me to "immortality"&#8212;I have been <unclear reason="illegible" cert="high" resp="#al">through every</unclear>thing except <hi rend="underline">revival religion</hi> or positive <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">"knowledge of</unclear> God") Walt! I think Native <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">minds are for</unclear> a "Philosopher" and (<hi rend="underline">therefore</hi> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">skeptics</unclear>", but <hi rend="underline">circumstances</hi> have made me <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> and <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> long time a believer <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">in</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> of <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">one</unclear> sort or other. (Please <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">don't</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> other <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> <hi rend="underline">hunter come down</hi> <gap reason="illegible" extent="five or six words"/> my <hi rend="underline">dilapidated <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">devillry</unclear></hi> <!-- or "dwelling" -NNK--> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/></p>

            <note type="authorial" place="bottom" anchored="true"> I think I would like to read <gap reason="illegible" extent="three or four words"/><unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">Life</unclear>&#8212;have you seen it?&#8212;<gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> about <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> <hi rend="underline">health</hi> and continuance <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">of</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/></note>
                
            <closer>
                <signed>John Newton Johnson <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/> <!-- looks like "Ala" at the end of the letter -NNK --> </signed>
